summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of the westerly 50 feet of Lot 2 of revised King County Short Plat No. 1176075; portion of the southeast quarter of the northwest quarter of Section 6, Township 23 North, Range 4 East (Also known as Lots 3 and 4, Block 1, McCarthy's Alder Grove Addition); the east 20 feet of 3rd Avenue North from the north margin of the Alley in Block 79 Denny and Hoyt's Supplemental Plat; the west half of the north 100 feet of vacated 14th Avenue south as measured along the west margin thereof, in the southeast quarter of Section 32, Township 24 North, Range 4 East W.M., lying south of the south limited access line of Primary State Highway No. 1.
